<h2>decktech.net</h2><b>location of article:</b> <hr>Magi Nation Duel - now in Japanese! posted by DeckTech on Sat May 18 2002 <br>That's right, you can now get your MND cards in Japanese.  Magi Nation Duel is famous for it's outstanding manga art, and what better way to get into the feel than with Japanese versions of your favorite cards!<br>
<br>
This is a big step for our rising star here on DT, and are sure to be popular both abroad and here.<br>
<br>
Not only that but a manga serial is also planned!<br>
<br>
Congratulations II<br>
