Reprint of article found at <a href="http://www.magi-nation.com/MNDJapan.html" target="x">http://www.magi-nation.com/MNDJapan.html</a> <br>
---------------------------------<br>
     At the Tokyo Toy Fair (May 9-12, 2002), Interactive Imagination Corp and Epoch Company Ltd announced plans to launch Magi-Nation Duel this summer. Planned 2002 releases include: Serialized Magi-Nation manga in Kodansha&#8217;s Comic Bon Bon premiering in July, Magi-Nation Base Set Starters and Boosters in August, followed by the Awakening Expansion by year&#8217;s end. Plus, the official Japanese debut of Magi-Nation will be augmented with ancillary products such as action figures, stickers, pins and other collectible items. Planned releases will be supported by organized gaming events throughout the course of the year.  <br>
    Following the launch announcement, potential licensees lined up to express their excitement and enthusiasm for the anticipated success of Magi-Nation in the Japanese market. <br>
